				Keep copies of the letter on hand for your clients.  </p>
				<p class="directive">  To ensure that your clients have a safe and enjoyable trip when they are travelling with children, consult our <a href="/travelling/children/children-travel" target="_blank">Children and travel</a> page and recommend it to them.</p>

